data.description: Spacious 4BD 2BA property located on a corner lot on a very charming, and quiet street. Home has been updated and very well maintained. Some updates include: newer stainless steel appliances, new carpet on the lower level, new hot water heater, and updated landscaping! Lower level features a recreation room, and laundry area. Also has a wonderful outdoor patio with views of our beautiful city and Mill Mountain Star! Convenient to restaurants, shopping, medical facilities, and I581!
